luation in IPO\"","line":32},{"title":"for investor speculation","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2026-04-06/spacex-mega-ipos-signal-caution-for-stock-market-bulls \"OPINION: SpaceX Heralds New Era of Mega IPOs. Buyers Beware\"","line":32},{"title":"established a Mars colony","target":"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/08/10/why-spacex-investors-arent-concerned-about-elon-taking-tesla-private.html \"Why SpaceX investors aren’t concerned about Musk taking Tesla private\"","line":32},{"title":"about $400 billion","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-07-08/spacex-valuation-said-to-hit-around-400-billion-in-share-sale \"SpaceX Valuation to Hit Around $400 Billion in Share Sale\"","line":34},{"title":"according to Bloomberg Intelligence","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/spacex-is-said-to-target-more-than-2-trillion-valuation-in-ipo","line":34},{"title":"about $16 billion last year","target":"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1929950051415273504?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1929950051415273504%7Ctwgr%5Eeb5514cc00858bd6109af859c3c207d580191ec4%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-06-03%2Fspacex-2025-revenue-is-around-15-5-billion-musk-says \"X Post: Elon Musk\"","line":34},{"title":"complained that its prices are too high","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-08-07/elon-musk-s-starlink-satellite-service-loses-its-shine-with-consumers-in-kenya \"Starlink Is Losing Subscribers in Once-Thriving Kenyan Market\"","line":36},{"title":"about 10 million","target":"https://x.com/Starlink/status/2022446814591615013 \"X Post: Starlink\"","line":36},{"title":"a bit choppy","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-07-06/trump-derides-musk-s-third-political-party-plan-as-bound-to-fail \"Trump Slams Musk Plan for Rival Party as Feud Deepens\"","line":38},{"title":"White House event in 2022","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-22/citizen-elon-podcast-traces-musk-s-path-to-campaigning-for-donald-trump \"Elon Musk’s Political Awakening Has Roots in Grievance\"","line":38},{"title":"SpaceX’s valuation had doubled to $800 billion","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-13/spacex-sets-insider-share-deal-at-about-800-billion-valuation \"SpaceX Sets $800 Billion Valuation, Confirms 2026 IPO Plans\"","line":42},{"title":"yet another valuation upgrade","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-02/elon-musk-s-spacex-said-to-combine-with-xai-ahead-of-mega-ipo \"Musk’s SpaceX Combines With xAI at $1.25 Trillion Valuation\"","line":42},{"title":"if they want a piece of the IPO","target":"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/business/spacex-ipo-grok-elon-musk.html \"Big Banks Seeking a Piece of SpaceX’s I.P.O. Must Subscribe to Elon Musk’s Grok\"","line":44},{"title":"crowdsourced Robotaxi Tracker","target":"https://robotaxitracker.com/?provider=tesla&area=austin \"Robotaxi Tracker\"","line":48},{"title":"claimed revenue of $2 billion a month","target":"https://openai.com/index/accelerating-the-next-phase-ai/ \"OpenAI raises $122 billion to accelerate the next phase of AI\"","line":50},{"title":"about $100 million in revenue","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-01-09/musk-s-xai-reports-higher-quarterly-loss-plans-to-power-optimus \"Musk’s xAI Burns Almost $8 Billion, Reveals Optimus Plan\"","line":50},{"title":"public-market investors to focus on a futuristic sales pitch","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/spacex-s-ipo-pitch-centers-on-elon-musk-s-ability-to-sell-the-dream \"SpaceX’s IPO Pitch Centers on Elon Musk’s Ability to ‘Sell the Dream’\"","line":50}],"metadata":{"title":"The SpaceX IPO Is Elon Musk’s Most Audacious Product Launch Yet","source":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/elon-musk-spacex-ipo-2-trillion-valuation-push-explained?srnd=homepage-americas","author":["[[Max Chafkin]]"],"published":"2026-04-08","created":"2026-04-08","description":"Its $2 trillion valuation leans heavily on AI hype.","tags":["#clippings"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:Clippings/The SpaceX IPO Is Elon Musk’s Most Audacious Product Launch Yet.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1l975e8","at":1775663949282},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.02785177,-0.02043263,0.04722819,-0.05260237,-0.01326368,0.01037033,-0.01400846,0.06779063,0.03852896,0.00077875,0.04515337,-0.0380445,0.03019542,0.03085773,0.05093598,-0.07527237,0.03053804,-0.04635789,-0.04500569,0.0352601,0.13447104,-0.04467303,-0.00727155,-0.10171248,0.08483009,0.03995159,-0.04913564,-0.03868102,-0.06047964,-0.21693811,0.0020292,-0.02620182,0.09625005,0.01724514,0.02108868,-0.02825691,0.03801599,-0.01187048,-0.01358863,0.02833312,0.01002612,-0.00215419,-0.04350122,0.03314753,0.01670591,-0.06872834,0.01771244,-0.03093425,0.02334057,0.03191186,-0.02202248,-0.0184503,0.01945015,-0.00020917,0.04453536,-0.01946964,-0.05212323,0.03946119,0.02823165,0.06028795,0.03875085,0.00317054,-0.20356786,0.09580818,0.07057317,-0.0196356,-0.01203278,-0.06092121,-0.03601516,-0.04833896,0.08605803,0.03858402,-0.01053445,0.02418032,-0.0124746,-0.02926882,0.04663344,-0.02895001,-0.04696758,-0.04697536,0.01039788,-0.00204052,-0.05955285,0.01667059,-0.04146199,0.02988448,0.04881852,-0.00132036,0.06229984,0.04526411,-0.02863202,0.00489138,0.04895028,0.01626565,-0.03981911,0.04739332,0.05489126,-0.02562488,-0.03837825,0.11364252,-0.01466491,0.03259428,0.00795552,-0.04643667,0.09351154,-0.04419005,-0.01866291,0.01303685,-0.01946952,-0.00524062,0.02199974,0.0055063,0.09818582,-0.01674514,0.00687907,0.01633153,0.00676162,0.00851294,0.01672442,-0.04294321,-0.02634598,0.00531186,0.04840443,-0.02371088,0.00908552,-0.00770514,0.06553058,0.02831567,-0.00256283,0.01580686,0.03218623,0.00059243,-0.03723617,-0.00505658,-0.00496247,-0.00993443,-0.00655161,-0.00955501,0.01390188,0.0