.com/news/articles/2025-07-08/spacex-valuation-said-to-hit-around-400-billion-in-share-sale \"SpaceX Valuation to Hit Around $400 Billion in Share Sale\"","line":7},{"title":"according to Bloomberg Intelligence","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/spacex-is-said-to-target-more-than-2-trillion-valuation-in-ipo","line":7},{"title":"about $16 billion last year","target":"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1929950051415273504?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1929950051415273504%7Ctwgr%5Eeb5514cc00858bd6109af859c3c207d580191ec4%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-06-03%2Fspacex-2025-revenue-is-around-15-5-billion-musk-says \"X Post: Elon Musk\"","line":7},{"title":"complained that its prices are too high","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-08-07/elon-musk-s-starlink-satellite-service-loses-its-shine-with-consumers-in-kenya \"Starlink Is Losing Subscribers in Once-Thriving Kenyan Market\"","line":9},{"title":"about 10 million","target":"https://x.com/Starlink/status/2022446814591615013 \"X Post: Starlink\"","line":9},{"title":"a bit choppy","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-07-06/trump-derides-musk-s-third-political-party-plan-as-bound-to-fail \"Trump Slams Musk Plan for Rival Party as Feud Deepens\"","line":11},{"title":"White House event in 2022","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-22/citizen-elon-podcast-traces-musk-s-path-to-campaigning-for-donald-trump \"Elon Musk’s Political Awakening Has Roots in Grievance\"","line":11},{"title":"SpaceX’s valuation had doubled to $800 billion","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-13/spacex-sets-insider-share-deal-at-about-800-billion-valuation \"SpaceX Sets $800 Billion Valuation, Confirms 2026 IPO Plans\"","line":15},{"title":"yet another valuation upgrade","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-02/elon-musk-s-spacex-said-to-combine-with-xai-ahead-of-mega-ipo \"Musk’s SpaceX Combines With xAI at $1.25 Trillion Valuation\"","line":15},{"title":"if they want a piece of the IPO","target":"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/business/spacex-ipo-grok-elon-musk.html \"Big Banks Seeking a Piece of SpaceX’s I.P.O. Must Subscribe to Elon Musk’s Grok\"","line":17},{"title":"crowdsourced Robotaxi Tracker","target":"https://robotaxitracker.com/?provider=tesla&area=austin \"Robotaxi Tracker\"","line":21},{"title":"claimed revenue of $2 billion a month","target":"https://openai.com/index/accelerating-the-next-phase-ai/ \"OpenAI raises $122 billion to accelerate the next phase of AI\"","line":23},{"title":"about $100 million in revenue","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-01-09/musk-s-xai-reports-higher-quarterly-loss-plans-to-power-optimus \"Musk’s xAI Burns Almost $8 Billion, Reveals Optimus Plan\"","line":23},{"title":"public-market investors to focus on a futuristic sales pitch","target":"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/spacex-s-ipo-pitch-centers-on-elon-musk-s-ability-to-sell-the-dream \"SpaceX’s IPO Pitch Centers on Elon Musk’s Ability to ‘Sell the Dream’\"","line":23}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
